Umm Kulthum reigned the world of Arabic music for over half a century./After 
publishing his theory of relativity, Einstein reigned the world of physics./Car man­
ufacturers are competing to reign in the world of the electric vehicles market. 
 ِهِﻮاد َﺟ ِةَﻮْﮭَﺻ ْﻦَﻋ َﻞﱠﺟَ َﺮﺗ
To honourably die or be killed; to dismount from a horse; to honourably 
retire, depart, or step out of a position . 
